    17Ôćĺ// runSessionStart outputs JSON with systemMessage (visible banner) and
    18Ôćĺ// additionalContext (LLM context) for the SessionStart hook.
    19Ôćĺ// Also captures the session in DB + log.
    20Ôćĺfunc runSessionStart() error {
